resources.string: Welcome to ‘THE TUITION’ an online platform for the students. Here, we are providing you Practice Papers, MCQ’s and Test Papers with their solutions without spending even a single penny so that you can practice and learn more. This is helpful for you to analyse yourself time to time. Moreover, we will also provide the videos of chapters based on NCERT syllabus and some other books like R.S. Agarwal, Composite Mathematics, R.D. Sharma etc. The explanations of these Practice Papers, MCQ’s and Test Papers will be provided in the videos on my Youtube channel.
